casebody.data:
Leon Canady v. Victor Liburdi, Warden (11383)

Dupont, C. J., O’Connell and Schaller, Js.

Argued April 26 decision released May 18, 1993 Temmy Ann Pieszak, assistant public defender, for the appellant (petitioner). Leah Hawley, assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were Michael Dearington, state’s attorney, and Eva Lenczewski, assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (respondent). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
